00:08:53.053 --> 00:09:09.053
Which guarantees you that you can take your virtual machines as they are today, the VM images, or your containers, and then run them in an environment which is confidential computing. And the way it manifests is following. You go to your cloud provider, Azure.


62
00:09:09.053 --> 00:09:24.053
GCP, IBM, Oracle in preview today. you say, hey, you get a VM instance, you know, whatever instance you have, 26 vCPUs with 128 gigabit RAM, right?


